Supplementary Package License

Code in `scripts/` and `src/` is provided under the MIT License.

Derived audit records in `data/`, `records/`, `configs/`, `schemas/`, and
`manifests/` are provided for anonymous peer review and research
reproduction. These records do not include raw ImageNet images, pretrained
checkpoints, linear-head checkpoints, private data, or cluster logs.

Pretrained encoders and datasets are not redistributed in this package. Users
must obtain them from the original providers and follow their licenses and
terms of use.

